December has been a real treat ♥️
Red Bull Arena is home to @tierna_davidson! 😤🖤

To Chicago: the beautiful place that fostered my evolution from a young college player into a real professional. The home of my dream, my friends, and the first step in my adult life. You welcomed me with open arms. Through the pretty and the ugly, you challenged me to learn and mature in ways I didn’t know were possible. 

To my teammates, past and present: Thank you. Your belief in me over the past five years encouraged me to grow in so many ways. Every year we pushed through new obstacles, continuing to grow together and defy the boundaries of what anyone thought was possible for us. The small moments in between the milestones are the ones that I will cherish the most. You are—and will continue to be—the reason I show up every day. 

Thank you to the fans, to the Red Stars organization, and to my family for sticking by me throughout my journey thus far. Your support has allowed me to develop both my ability and my identity. I feel so at peace remembering my time in Chicago as I take this next step in my career. Thank you for everything.
